---
import DocsLayout from '../../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
---

<DocsLayout title="aura gas">
  <nav class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-zinc-500 mb-8">
    <a href="/docs" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Docs</a>
    <span>/</span>
    <a href="/docs/commands" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Commands</a>
    <span>/</span>
    <span class="text-white">aura gas</span>
  </nav>

  <div class="mb-12">
    <div class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-zinc-800 text-xs font-mono text-zinc-400 inline-block mb-4">command</div>
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4 font-mono">aura gas</h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-zinc-400">Real-time gas price monitoring across multiple networks.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="glass-card p-6 mb-12">
    <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Synopsis</h3>
    <div class="terminal">
      <div class="p-4 font-mono text-sm">
        <span class="text-green-400">aura gas</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="mb-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Description</h2>
    <p class="text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
      The <code class="px-2 py-1 bg-zinc-800 rounded text-green-400">aura gas</code> command fetches current gas prices from all supported blockchain networks. 
      It's designed to help you time your transactions perfectly by comparing costs between Ethereum Mainnet and various L2s like Base or zkSync.
    </p>
    <p class="text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed">
      Every successful query is automatically synchronized with your <strong>Aura Dashboard</strong>, allowing you to track gas trends over time.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Output Breakdown</h2>
    <div class="terminal mb-6">
      <div class="terminal-header">
        <div class="terminal-dot bg-red-500"></div>
        <div class="terminal-dot bg-yellow-500"></div>
        <div class="terminal-dot bg-green-500"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="p-4 font-mono text-sm space-y-1">
        <div><span class="text-purple-400">❯</span> <span class="text-green-400">aura gas</span></div>
        <div class="text-zinc-500 mt-2">Fetching gas prices from multiple networks...</div>
        <div class="text-zinc-300">Ethereum Mainnet: <span class="text-yellow-400">12.4501 Gwei</span></div>
        <div class="text-zinc-300">Base: <span class="text-green-400">0.0052 Gwei</span></div>
        <div class="text-zinc-300">Arbitrum One: <span class="text-green-400">0.0180 Gwei</span></div>
        <div class="text-zinc-300">zkSync Era: <span class="text-green-400">0.0110 Gwei</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="glass-card p-5 border-l-4 border-green-500">
        <h4 class="text-white font-bold mb-2">L2 Optimized</h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">Displays up to 4 decimal places for Layer 2 networks where gas prices are often extremely low.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="glass-card p-5 border-l-4 border-blue-500">
        <h4 class="text-white font-bold mb-2">Dashboard Sync</h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">Sends the latest data to your web interface for central monitoring.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Technical Details</h2>
    <p class="text-zinc-300 mb-6">
      Aura uses high-performance RPC endpoints defined in your configuration to query the <code>getGasPrice</code> method on each chain.
    </p>
    <div class="glass-card p-4">
      <h4 class="text-xs font-mono uppercase mb-2 text-center text-zinc-200">Supported Networks</h4>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 justify-center">
        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-zinc-800 rounded-full text-xs">Ethereum</span>
        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-zinc-800 rounded-full text-xs">Base</span>
        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-zinc-800 rounded-full text-xs">Arbitrum</span>
        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-zinc-800 rounded-full text-xs">Optimism</span>
        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-zinc-800 rounded-full text-xs">zkSync Era</span>
        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-zinc-800 rounded-full text-xs">BSC</span>
        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-zinc-800 rounded-full text-xs">Polygon</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="pt-8 border-t border-zinc-800/50">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-between text-sm text-zinc-500">
      <a href="/docs/commands/chat" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">← aura chat</a>
      <a href="/docs/commands/tx" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">aura tx →</a>
    </div>
  </footer>
</DocsLayout>
